{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 51,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الذَّارِيَاتِ",
    "englishName": "Adh-Dhaariyat",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Winnowing Winds",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 60,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4676,
        "text": "By the (Winds) that scatter broadcast;",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4677,
        "text": "And those that lift and bear away heavy weights;",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4678,
        "text": "And those that flow with ease and gentleness;",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4679,
        "text": "And those that distribute and apportion by Command;-",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4680,
        "text": "Verily that which ye are promised is true;",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4681,
        "text": "And verily Judgment and Justice must indeed come to pass.",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4682,
        "text": "By the Sky with (its) numerous Paths,",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4683,
        "text": "Truly ye are in a doctrine discordant,",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4684,
        "text": "Through which are deluded (away from the Truth) such as would be deluded.",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4685,
        "text": "Woe to the falsehood-mongers,-",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4686,
        "text": "Those who (flounder) heedless in a flood of confusion:",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4687,
        "text": "They ask, \"When will be the Day of Judgment and Justice?\"",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4688,
        "text": "(It will be) a Day when they will be tried (and tested) over the Fire!",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4689,
        "text": "\"Taste ye your trial! This is what ye used to ask to be hastened!\"",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4690,
        "text": "As to the Righteous, they will be in the midst of Gardens and Springs,",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4691,
        "text": "Taking joy in the things which their Lord gives them, because, before then, they lived a good life.",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4692,
        "text": "They were in the habit of sleeping but little by night,",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4693,
        "text": "And in the hour of early dawn, they (were found) praying for Forgiveness;",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4694,
        "text": "And in their wealth and possessions (was remembered) the right of the (needy,) him who asked, and him who (for some reason) was prevented (from asking).",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4695,
        "text": "On the earth are signs for those of assured Faith,",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4696,
        "text": "As also in your own selves: Will ye not then see?",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4697,
        "text": "And in heaven is your Sustenance, as (also) that which ye are promised.",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4698,
        "text": "Then, by the Lord of heaven and earth, this is the very Truth, as much as the fact that ye can speak intelligently to each other.",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4699,
        "text": "Has the story reached thee, of the honoured guests of Abraham?",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4700,
        "text": "Behold, they entered his presence, and said: \"Peace!\" He said, \"Peace!\" (and thought, \"These seem) unusual people.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4701,
        "text": "Then he turned quickly to his household, brought out a fatted calf,",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4702,
        "text": "And placed it before them.. he said, \"Will ye not eat?\"",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4703,
        "text": "(When they did not eat), He conceived a fear of them. They said, \"Fear not,\" and they gave him glad tidings of a son endowed with knowledge.",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4704,
        "text": "But his wife came forward (laughing) aloud: she smote her forehead and said: \"A barren old woman!\"",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4705,
        "text": "They said, \"Even so has thy Lord spoken: and He is full of Wisdom and Knowledge.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4706,
        "text": "(Abraham) said: \"And what, O ye Messengers, is your errand (now)?\"",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4707,
        "text": "They said, \"We have been sent to a people (deep) in sin;-",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4708,
        "text": "\"To bring on, on them, (a shower of) stones of clay (brimstone),",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4709,
        "text": "\"Marked as from thy Lord for those who trespass beyond bounds.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4710,
        "text": "Then We evacuated those of the Believers who were there,",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4711,
        "text": "But We found not there any just (Muslim) persons except in one house:",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4712,
        "text": "And We left there a Sign for such as fear the Grievous Penalty.",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4713,
        "text": "And in Moses (was another Sign): Behold, We sent him to Pharaoh, with authority manifest.",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4714,
        "text": "But (Pharaoh) turned back with his Chiefs, and said, \"A sorcerer, or one possessed!\"",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4715,
        "text": "So We took him and his forces, and threw them into the sea; and his was the blame.",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4716,
        "text": "And in the 'Ad (people) (was another Sign): Behold, We sent against them the devastating Wind:",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4717,
        "text": "It left nothing whatever that it came up against, but reduced it to ruin and rottenness.",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4718,
        "text": "And in the Thamud (was another Sign): Behold, they were told, \"Enjoy (your brief day) for a little while!\"",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4719,
        "text": "But they insolently defied the Command of their Lord: So the stunning noise (of an earthquake) seized them, even while they were looking on.",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4720,
        "text": "Then they could not even stand (on their feet), nor could they help themselves.",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4721,
        "text": "So were the People of Noah before them for they wickedly transgressed.",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4722,
        "text": "With power and skill did We construct the Firmament: for it is We Who create the vastness of pace.",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4723,
        "text": "And We have spread out the (spacious) earth: How excellently We do spread out!",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4724,
        "text": "And of every thing We have created pairs: That ye may receive instruction.",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4725,
        "text": "Hasten ye then (at once) to Allah: I am from Him a Warner to you, clear and open!",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4726,
        "text": "And make not another an object of worship with Allah: I am from Him a Warner to you, clear and open!",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4727,
        "text": "Similarly, no messenger came to the Peoples before them, but they said (of him) in like manner, \"A sorcerer, or one possessed\"!",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4728,
        "text": "Is this the legacy they have transmitted, one to another? Nay, they are themselves a people transgressing beyond bounds!",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4729,
        "text": "So turn away from them: not thine is the blame.",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4730,
        "text": "But teach (thy Message) for teaching benefits the Believers.",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4731,
        "text": "I have only created Jinns and men, that they may serve Me.",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4732,
        "text": "No Sustenance do I require of them, nor do I require that they should feed Me.",
        "numberInSurah": 57,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4733,
        "text": "For Allah is He Who gives (all) Sustenance,- Lord of Power,- Steadfast (for ever).",
        "numberInSurah": 58,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4734,
        "text": "For the Wrong-doers, their portion is like unto the portion of their fellows (of earlier generations): then let them not ask Me to hasten (that portion)!",
        "numberInSurah": 59,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4735,
        "text": "Woe, then, to the Unbelievers, on account of that Day of theirs which they have been promised!",
        "numberInSurah": 60,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
    "edition": {
      "identifier": "en.yusufali",
      "language": "en",
      "name": "Yusuf Ali",
      "englishName": "Abdullah Yusuf Ali",
      "format": "text",
      "type": "translation",
      "direction": "ltr"
    }
  }
}